headline: Prediction: These 2 Stocks Will Crush the S&P 500 Over the Next 3 Years
summary: The stock market has gotten off to a bumpy start in 2025, with the S&P 500 index down sharply.  On the other hand, taking a buy-and-hold approach to great companies on the heels of recent valuation discounts could open the door for patient investors to see very strong returns.  With that in mind, read on to see why two Motley Fool contributors think that these stocks below will crush the S&P 500 over the next three years.
